{
  "stem": "24411.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they said, you have no place where to run here.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There's no way you could survive.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That's-- they let us go.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "About three hours.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But there was no place to go.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We saw farms.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We stole a lot of potatoes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We see if nobody looks.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And cabbage.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They took away from us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was dogs, a lot of dogs.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They start to bark.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's it.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We said, we go-- we just went to the farms to get some food.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Walking.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They took us.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nothing happened.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Nothing.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We cried, and that's it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The other people was said, in a way, we're glad you're back.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But we were very happy if you would make it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But there was no way you could make that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There was no way.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I didn't think anything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Just crying, and I went to sleep.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's all.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nothing happened.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Just you know, when-- and the-- we went out, and there was-- in the summertime, it was better.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We went out, and we saw each other.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We talked.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And everybody said, we're going to survive, and it's going to be OK.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that's all.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But-- that's it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When-- we've all forgot about this, but a lot of people knew, remembered.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was Rosh Hashana, Yom Kippur.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were fasting, and we didn't go out to work.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they make it go to work.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And who didn't go out, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] they took me in for three days to jail, without food-- with no-- it was like-- like a hole with no windows.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There was a pail if you have to make.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And for three days and three nights, then when I-- when they took me out, I couldn't see anything.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was very dark.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
